{"body": "An applicant\u2019s capital is to be treated as yielding\u2014\na monthly income of \u00a34.35 for each \u00a3250 in excess of \u00a36,000 and \u00a34.35 for any excess which is not a complete \u00a3250, or\na weekly income of \u00a31 for each \u00a3250 in excess of \u00a36,000 and \u00a31 for any excess which is not a complete \u00a3250.\nParagraph (1) does not apply where the capital is disregarded or the actual income from that capital is taken into account under regulation 57(1)(j) (income from an annuity) or 57(1)(k) (income from a trust).\nWhere an applicant\u2019s capital is treated as yielding income, any actual income derived from that capital, for example rental, interest or dividends, is to be treated as part of the applicant\u2019s capital from the day it is due to be paid to the applicant.", "citation_label": "SSI 2021/249 reg. 63", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/ssi/2021/249/63", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital", "heading": "Regulation 63", "id": "76306621-e7af-5441-9d82-f96375b45dca", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "249", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "63", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "ssi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2021"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "regulation", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "SSI 2021/249 reg. 63", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": ["S"], "references_to": ["ssi/2021/249"], "retrieved_at": null}, "ordinal": 63, "source_as_of": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital", "source_document_id": "ssi/2021/249", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2021/249/regulation/63", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital/ssi/2021/249/regulation-63.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2021/249/regulation/63", "version": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital"}
{"body": "No person is entitled to council tax reduction if that person\u2019s capital exceeds \u00a316,000.", "citation_label": "SSI 2021/249 reg. 66", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/ssi/2021/249/66", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital", "heading": "Regulation 66", "id": "17e19e3a-4b7f-5df7-91b8-852b5d386c13", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "249", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "66", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "ssi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2021"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "regulation", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "SSI 2021/249 reg. 66", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": ["S"], "references_to": ["ssi/2021/249"], "retrieved_at": null}, "ordinal": 66, "source_as_of": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital", "source_document_id": "ssi/2021/249", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2021/249/regulation/66", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital/ssi/2021/249/regulation-66.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2021/249/regulation/66", "version": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital"}
